# Per-machine Claude Code permission allowlist. Local-only by design:
# entries can include literal command patterns with credentials embedded
# (Bearer tokens, API keys) approved interactively during a session, and
# committing those to git history is unrecoverable. Track team-wide
# Claude config in .claude/settings.json instead, never .local.json.
.claude/settings.local.jsondocs/draft_review/datasette_contacts_raw.json
